rule (modulo E) ProvisionerSendRandom:
   [ ProvisionerSendConfirm( pkP, pkD, dh, ck, ~Np, auth ), In( Cd ) ]
  --[ ProvisionerSendRandom( pkP, pkD, dh, ck, ~Np, Cd, auth ) ]->
   [ ProvisionerSendRandom( pkP, pkD, dh, ck, ~Np, Cd, auth ), Out( ~Np ) ]

  /* has exactly the trivial AC variant */

